{"tid":912111,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[燥] 打電話去馬會落注","createTime":"2018-11-22T12:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T12:49:44.000Z","uid":63588,"like":16,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5952880b8ab4c0ff6e30ab649290ca41b93bca66","tid":912111,"uid":63588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T12:02:18.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我不嬲都有賭馬既習慣<br />\n可以一邊工作一邊有啲野玩<br />\n早幾日跑馬日嘅第二場打電話落注聽到個好熟嘅聲<br />\n都冇咩點理啦<br />\n我一輪嘴講幾穿幾 第幾關買咩買咩 一口氣講完<br />\n條撚樣話只係第4日番工 大佬點落阿<br />\n仲夠膽問我：先生可唔可以重複一次<br />\n咁我緊係開始黎料啦<br />\n即刻開佢波<br />\n快撚啲啦 咁都聽唔鳩到 屌你老母之類個啲<br />\n佢燥燥地就覆番我 啱架啦啱架啦大家咁話啦<br />\n丫我屌佢老母<br />\n如果佢係我個仔我實劈撚死佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d0e2c5293389e9eff8eb5090094b7dfe9218c1","tid":912111,"uid":4562,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T12:03:54.000Z","msg":"好撚好笑牙"},{"pid":"d3cf95a80a256c2330aff3901fc5cec89a7416a8","tid":912111,"uid":202192,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T12:06:01.000Z","msg":"多咗啦"},{"pid":"dafd596b84dceccd59d1f00237ed155d39a2c487","tid":912111,"uid":15552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T12:08:19.000Z","msg":"好撚好笑？"},{"pid":"ddfe96962bd79287f5d3f68ed29d0b84a7d4498b","tid":912111,"uid":212760,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T12:12:46.000Z","msg":"我都冇講出口話第4日番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ca0e3d86a65bceee8324e434759905bf5fd646","tid":912111,"uid":69213,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T12:13:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3a044e90f995e08d21bdc1661e4bc71f271f0be","tid":912111,"uid":40636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T12:14:36.000Z